snippet.title: Mr Orange Trailer
snippet.description:
Play an exciting puzzle game based on physical mechanics, together with Mr Orange!
 
The goal is to help Mr Orange to reach an orange block , eliminating all obstacles along his way.
Play the game with your children for absolutely free! Discover new levels, learn new colored blocks.
Solve puzzles faster and earn stars.

Features:
 - Play for free
 - The puzzle game is easy to play
 - 30 levels of varying complexity, variety of colored blocks
 - The game is for children and adults
 - Play on phones and tablets, play at home and in the office, play anywhere

and enjoy the game!

Your feedback will help to make the game better. Write to us, share your opinion.
